Unreleased
	* Docs: add an "Unreleased" section to `whatsnew.md` and note the ONNX/
	  packaging (`pyproject.toml`/pixi, Python 3.10-3.14) changes in the 1.6.0
	  entry; remove the dead Universal Analytics config from `mkdocs.yml`
	* Fix output-directory READMEs (`macrel/output.py`): correct the abundance
	  output filename (`macrel.out.abundance.txt`, not the double-`.out`
	  `macrel.out.out.abundance.txt`), stop claiming the `percontigs` table has a
	  `Sample` row (the sample total is only in the `#`-comment header), and drop
	  the non-existent 10-aa lower bound from the smORFs description
	* Fix docs: correct thread-count and per-contig example-path claims in
	  `usage.md`; update `index.md` (pyrodigal instead of prodigal, ONNX-shipped
	  models, modlAMP-adapted descriptors, clustering marked optional); pin
	  conda channels and add the optional MMSeqs2/HMMER note in `install.md`;
	  clarify peptide-length bounds and document non-standard-residue handling
	  in `faq.md`
	* Fix docs: correct the `usage.md` flag reference (document `--output`/`-o`
	  instead of `--out`, list `get-examples`, note `--file-output` also works
	  for `query-ampsphere`, fix the `--mem`/`--cluster`/`--keep-fasta-headers`
	  descriptions, correct the `--fasta`/`--reads` subcommand scopes, and add
	  the `--verbose`/`--quiet` and AMPSphere query flags)
	* Fix AMP-density tutorial: refresh the stale `expected.density` table to
	  match the current (ONNX) model predictions, write the grouped table with
	  `index=True` so the `taxonomy` column is retained, and cross-reference the
	  built-in sample-wide density
	* Accept `--outtag` as an alias for `--tag` (matches the docs and help examples)
	* Fix docs: AMPSphere HMMER mode is `--query-mode=hmmer` (not `hmm`) and
	  example-output paths live under `tests/` (not `test/`)
	* Drop the unused `tzlocal` dependency (from `pyproject.toml` and the docs)
	* Fix crash in `get-smorfs --file-output` when writing the README
	* Fix missing `import sys` in ampsphere.py error paths
	* Fix wrong accession returned by local M-stripped exact match in ampsphere.py
	* Fix `parse_args` ignoring its argument, breaking programmatic invocation
	* Add missing `pyrodigal` dependency to `pyproject.toml`
	* Align Python-version claims on 3.10+ across docs/comments
	* Use `requests` with error handling for `get-examples` downloads
	* URL-encode sequences in remote AMPSphere queries
	* Check HTTP status on all AMPSphere API requests and downloads
	* Add missing newline to the `--force` "output folder already exists" warning
	* Support `--file-output` for the `query-ampsphere` command
	* Skip empty sequences and sequences with non-standard amino acids during
	  feature computation (with a warning) instead of crashing
	* Avoid ZeroDivisionError in AMP-density calculation on empty input

